Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Important clues pointing to the true killer left behind by the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dying message...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guidepost to the truth from beyond the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:32.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only the light of deductions can tear apart\Nblack shadows and deep darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:36.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A case occurs at a ski resort?\NWhat's behind the victim's odd actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:42.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're not going to ski, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking in this nice, cloudless sky first...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the grandeur of this snowy white landscape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn. I knew I shouldn't have come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! You lost the key to the rental cabin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! It's all thanks to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess all we can do is call the manager to bring a duplicate key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any phone booths around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that cabin is still under construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the ski bus already left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing nearby is that one lodge up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, ask help from some upstart with a lodge there? Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice! We'll open it by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- No, don't!\N- Stop, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say! Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! It is Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:32.70,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama (53)\NTohto University Medical Professor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always read about your brilliant work in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a magnificent lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such an elegant color and design!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who was talking about rich upstarts just a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't heard your names yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.\NWe're watching him for a friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lion-shaped door decoration is superb, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for a horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I guess that was asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true. Horses would be better than lions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:22.21,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara (30)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are these folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, some friends I ran into just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're all doctors at the same university?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep! We're all assistants for Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctors are very factional, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:45.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa (48)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been studying under the doctor for dozens of years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I transferred here three years ago from some future-less professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:53.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita (31)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad to be where I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:59.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi (30)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:05:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The essay he presented the other day was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Gene Therapy as Treatment for Cancer of the Large Intestine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole medical school is praising his essay right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come now, with my brains, it was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I forgot to buy snacks to go with our drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go pick some up at the shop at the bottom of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you get some chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dried cuttlefish for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have a salad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Here, write it all down so I know what to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The convenience store closes before 10:00, so hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,8:58...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's addicted to a melodrama that gets 30% ratings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I watch that show, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are you off to, Dr. Tobita?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Night skiing. I haven't gotten my fix yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be back by around 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll take a nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,relaxing bath until the snacks arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:40.63,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait! Tsutomu{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:45.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have to, Mitsue{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}. We can never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:48.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, please! Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:51.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?! Why can't we be together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been rough with the sudden blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tobita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, can't possibly night ski with that blizzard out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That warms me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are we drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was your bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? I had asked for a salad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, they were sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was no ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who asked for ice cream in this weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was Dr. Oyama? He does love ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His TV drama ended at 10:00,\Nso where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama always tapes the show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and replays the best scenes afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:58.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn you... This was your original intent all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:02.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But you won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The great detective, Kogoro Mouri, is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:10.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure that he, if anyone, will get this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy always in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! My dad's a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's past 11:00 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's taking a bit too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go see what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's that famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks sure can be deceiving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's untie his ropes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:09:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you don't mess up the murder scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! They can't get police cars
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or an ambulance here in this blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so? Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I, the great Kogoro Mouri, will have to take charge here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're still so drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask just to be safe—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no one's touched anything in the room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing aside from Dr. Oyama's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found him first, Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume the same goes for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I saw him covered in blood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and fell down in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anything of value in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He does have a safe in the cabinet to the right of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all scratched up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what's inside this safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cash, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always carried large sums of money with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I guess they were after money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this blood trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's almost as if he crawled to the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why is he sitting formally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The blood on the table stops cleanly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah. The tablecloth slipped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Marks from the bloodied rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:25.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be a dying message from Dr. Oyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they used tape on the window to muffle the sound, then snuck in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were even nice enough to leave footprints outside the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've got this figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No "hmmms"! Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to ask, but could you examine him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As doctors, you're more qualified than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I estimate his time of death to be between 9:30 and 10:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So it was during his TV drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are countless cuts all over his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it appears he died of suffocation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after having both lungs punctured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suffocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, with holes in his lungs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't hold air to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably suffered terribly for 10 or 15 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was most likely done for monetary gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After breaking in through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the killer attacked and tied up\NDr. Oyama, who was watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then demanded the safe combination, but didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enraged, the culprit stabbed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and fled back out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh, talk about dense...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This man has a cool watch! It's all sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, he was tied up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he was super lucky the killer didn't take his gold watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd for someone after money to overlook a watch like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that the killer must be pretty stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you think the killer must've been gutsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Look at the footprints outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They come straight to this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I'd be afraid someone else was in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and would sneak around and peek in before going inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scratching the safe and tying Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} up was camouflage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,meant to make it look like this was about money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer knew Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be watching TV alone then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, one of you four is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's hear each of your alibis between 9:30 and 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:24.15,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara (30)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left at 9:00 and returned at around 9:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only snacks that were sold out were salad and ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you could've finished sooner if you rushed in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes over 40 minutes round-trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying, you can try it with my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:47.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita (31)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went night skiing, a ski slope also 40 minutes round-trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have proof of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lift ticket has today's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it even has the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:14:00.89,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi (30)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:14:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cleaned up and washed things with Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She only left for 2 or 3 minutes to throw out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa (48)\NTohto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a bath from 9:30 until shortly after 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:15.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's one other person besides Kanazawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} with a flimsy alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}B-Blood stains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:24.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? But why isn't there any blood on the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:27.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did someone put it here after the blood dried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:31.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute. The blood-smeared tablecloth... Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It matches perfectly! This lighter was sitting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:42.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, this afternoon, Oyama{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:46.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was hoping for a horse, but I guess that was asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:50.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was when he asked me and Ran our names...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:54.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! A horse! That's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:57.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This really is Oyama{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It explains his formal way of sitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:03.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the bloody lighter on the sofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And just as his dying message says,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the killer was that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister. There's something weird on the sofa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you damn kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! I ain't drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What, now?! What did you figure out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer. I just now figured out\Nwho stabbed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First is Tobita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who went night skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have made up a fake story\Nthat could be easily verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next is you, Ezumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only left Ran and Conan for 2 or 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not enough time to have killed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which only leaves Kanazawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} without alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I bought the snacks that everyone asked—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how much did it all cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't forget. You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you bought large amounts of all kinds of snacks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought them this afternoon when you bought the food for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the murder, you took everyone's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then pretended to leave in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then stopped somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pulled out the snacks they ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you had an alibi,\Nyou went and murdered Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid; you have no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you know yourself that there's proof
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:17:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in this room that you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a look at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood ends cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem like something was on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tablecloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please put it on the table so that it matches with the blood stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is this a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think back. Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died while sitting formally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should start to become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of your names includes characters used in shogi (Japanese chess).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:39.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:39.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:39.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:39.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:39.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Dr. Oyama always said how a horse would make the full set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You make up all the pieces but a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran. Take the lighter on the sofa and put it on the tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one place the blood on the lighter matches the tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kaori"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That is a lance's starting position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a dying message that gives your name, Kaori Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that before putting the tablecloth on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That square is the only one with long blood trails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was on the very edge of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just coincidentally turned out that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who tossed the tablecloth aside, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It must've happened when\Nthe killer and Dr. Oyama struggled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. The blood on the table ends cleanly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:19:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sofa the bloody lighter was on has no blood at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is proof that someone moved it after the blood dried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the killer must've returned to the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,noticed the message, and tossed it aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Kaori Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your undoing was that you noticed the message after you screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one other thing—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you said they were out of salad and ice cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but setting aside the salad, selling out of ice cream is—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that to him, Kaori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got along so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe he'd steal my paper from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paper? You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gene Therapy as Treatment for Cancer of the Large Intestine"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! He stole it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I had spent six whole years pouring my life into that essay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the paper I wrote for my late father's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father died of large intestinal cancer when I was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I became a doctor devoted to large intestinal cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was to prevent any more cases like my father's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, after he stole the paper I had finally completed, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:43.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody'll listen to you if you said you wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:48.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But society will pay attention if a famous professor makes it public!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:52.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure your father would be happier that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was then that I devised this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to kill the man who stomped on my feelings for my father
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by puncturing his lungs,\None of the worst ways to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never once imagined\Nhe would leave a dying message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,during those 10 to 15 minutes of agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was one mistake in your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had predicted the ice cream and salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were sold out of salad, but I did buy ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It melted inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had everyone's snacks ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told myself, "OK, time to kill him."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I suddenly thought back to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After spacing out for a while, the car's heater had melted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think his ice cream would trip me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:20.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dying messages. Sometimes, they're expressed in unusual ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got your angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your silver general is going to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now it's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:37.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sometimes, when you change your perspective of something ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:39.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Idiot"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
